Approach:

Problem Type: Extraction + reasoning

Input: Unstructured PDFs

Pipeline:

OCR (if required)

Structured extraction (NER / prompt-based)

Context enrichment (RAG)

Constraints:

High accuracy

Compliance (PII, healthcare regulations)

Metrics:

Extraction accuracy

Hallucination rate

💡 10. Key Insight

The primary failure point in GenAI systems is not model capability, but incorrect problem framing and lack of evaluation strategy.

